title: Pure Storage FlashArray: Overall Capacity
agents: pure_storage_fa
catalog: hw/storagehw/pure_storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors overall capacity and data reduction of a Pure Storage FlashArray.

 The default upper levels for used capacity are 80% (warn) and 90% (critical).
 They can be configured, together with lower levels for data reduction ratio, using the
 "Pure Storage Capacity" rule.

 To make this check work you have to configure the related special agent
 {Pure Storage FlashArray}.

discovery:
 One service is created.
